## 1. Project Overview

**Project Name:** W3B3 - Multi-Chain Staking & Yield Portal

**Description:**
W3B3 is a user-friendly web3 platform that enables users to:
- **Assess & discover** verified staking opportunities across chains
- **Stake capital** on stablecoins, memcoins, and web3 projects
- **Earn rewards** with automated distribution
- **Explore live portals** with real-time project metrics
- **Manage multi-chain portfolio** in one dashboard

**Target Users:**
- Retail crypto investors (primary)
- DeFi enthusiasts
- Yield farmers
- Memecoin traders looking for utility

**Key Value Proposition:**
- ONE dashboard for multi-chain staking
- Discover high-yield opportunities safely
- Transparent, audited smart contracts
- No KYC barriers (except when required by law)

